The CMQS-DEIM authors introduced modifications and additions including:

* curriculum epoch propagation from the training engine to the detector decoder;
* curriculum matching-aware query scoring and top-K query selection;
* DEIM-S and DEIM-L CMQS configurations;
* component ablation and hyperparameter configurations;
* computational profiling utilities;
* scale-wise query analysis and qualitative visualization tools;
* reproducibility documentation, result tables, and release scripts.

The associated manuscript is:

“Curriculum Matching-Aware Query Selection for Efficient End-to-End Object Detection”

submitted to The Visual Computer.

